short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Browse the old style MDN Web Docs.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Finally, we have a Chrome extension.

Users who like the old style of MDN Web Docs now have an option, a third-party hosting maintained by community users.

And you can use the extension to jump from the official site to the third-party hosting site, or vice versa.

Try it out now!

To contribute, go to: https://github.com/initdc/MDN-Wayback
